      <title>美联储卡什卡利称私人信贷可能降低系统性风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/fed-s-kashkari-says-private-credit-may-lessen-systemic-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[明尼阿波利斯联邦储备银行行长尼尔卡什卡利表示，尽管政治上缺乏增加银行资本要求的兴趣，但私人信贷市场的崛起可能降低美国金融体系的系统性风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/fed-s-kashkari-says-private-credit-may-lessen-systemic-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 00:24:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金持稳，因交易员权衡利率走势、缓解中东担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/gold-steady-as-traders-weigh-rate-path-easing-middle-east-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商消化了美国一位高级政策制定者暗示货币宽松步伐可能放缓的评论，黄金价格小幅下跌，而随着对中东冲突升级的担忧逐渐消退，避险需求下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/gold-steady-as-traders-weigh-rate-path-easing-middle-east-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 00:20:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MBK 称已获得大量股权，韩国锌业股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/korea-zinc-shares-gain-as-mbk-says-it-secured-substantial-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国锌业公司 (Korea Zinc Co.) 股价上涨 1.9%，此前收购公司 MBK Partners 表示，该公司已收购了足够多的股份，有助于其在备受关注的收购战中赢得对全球最大锌精炼厂的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/korea-zinc-shares-gain-as-mbk-says-it-secured-substantial-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 00:05:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
